        <title>Boolean Logic</title>
        
       <p>
            We can combine logic statement as well. Python also includes logical operators to combine or modify Booleans:

            <ol>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        <c>and</c>: <c>True</c> if both conditions are true
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        <c>or</c>: <c>True</c> if either condition is true (or both)
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        <c>not</c>: <c>True</c> if the condition is false
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ol>
